Comment: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Aiming to become an international actor.\N Vacation Abroad (Europe, America)\N Study Acting Abroad"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.99,0:00:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out! 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life, led lacking all splendor, is heading toward a climax. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious! 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come out of there! 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanuki-san is a woman with no faults on an emotional or visual level, 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but tonight she was just too... 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carry me away, before that person comes... 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.87,0:00:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-san is a silent, lovely maiden. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we are fated to be apart! 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we are not able to meet, then I cannot continue this relationship any longer. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.13,0:00:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko-san is classy and ladylike, but I can't see her like that! 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I choose Kaori-san! 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H6C00C6&\fad(200,0)}J{\c&H000000&}-pwq
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I was a brand-spanking new freshman university student 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and before me were held out circles' fliers far surpassing my own information intake potential. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And through each of them I could see a gateway to that rose-colored campus life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\c&H47FFFA&\3c&H8D2120&\be1\fad(100,0)}"Hero Show Association"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A four year moratorium. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it would be good to grant children's aggressive dreams once in a while. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And perhaps a raven-haired maiden that understands young boys' dreams may appear! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've turned over a new leaf! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, everyone... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Mochiguman... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never defeating anyone... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never hurting anyone... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you know it, trouble's quieted down... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's strong... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And has a big heart... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A great, big, sincere heart! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, save Mochiguman! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's the matter? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bad guys are trying to kidnap the girl, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, make them change their ways! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change your ways! Change your ways! Change your ways! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change your ways! Change your ways! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, they ran away! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, everyone! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Mochiguman intervened yet again! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mochiguman for you! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww... 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got knocked around pretty good there...\N And it's only 3,000 yen a performance. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to scout you. Big money guaranteed. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Order what you'd like at the engineering cafeteria and wait tomorrow at noon." 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds pretty fishy to me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for earlier. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spend my days in the Shimogamo Yuusuisou boarding house behind Eizan Demachiyanagi. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a three-story wooden building that looks like it could collapse at any time. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so run-down that just looking at it is worrisome. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it'll be an important cultural landmark soon, 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:05:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not difficult for me to imagine that no one would mind if it just vanished one day. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear viewers, be not surprised. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been exchanging letters with a girl after some strange happenings. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most crucial things about exchanging letters are that they be handwritten 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that you never meet your partner in correspondence, 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even should the very cauldron of hell be unleashed. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Far too oft that the elegant, precious 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,relationship you had fostered vanishes in an instant. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Higuchi Keiko-san, and I can tell her intelligence and education from her letters. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is surely my ideal woman. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what should I do? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it matter? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You speak of this to no one. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to keep it top secret. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I want you to be a certain woman's bodyguard. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bodyguard? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a dangerous job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to protect her while I am gone. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been some... trouble lately. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a great number of people who would try to deceive me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you, my friend, I can rely on without reservation. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as safe a bet as they come, yes? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you're a late bloomer that is exceedingly shy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore I have no need to worry about you doing anything... funny. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you handle this? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kaori. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori is a very elegant woman. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to be very courteous to her. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I do not wish the world at large to learn of our private matters. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you speak about this to others, then, for you... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name was Jougasaki, and he was the president of the movie circle Misogi. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He handed me Kaori's entertainment manual. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things like no direct contact, her favorite drinks, 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not to run out of sweets, show her movies to make sure she doesn't get bored... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the essential principles were written down. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm counting on you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go getting any weird thoughts, now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't think of her as a doll at all. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her hair was carefully combed, and her clothes were neat and elegant. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her makeup, and fingernails, and skin were all lovely... 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that elegant expression come from? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would be nice if Mr. Jougasaki came home soon, yes? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Jougasaki is really a very simple and good person, don't you think? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are beautiful... 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I can't understand how Mr. Jougasaki feels. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I do think I'd prefer a flesh and blood woman... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so the days where I would receive 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,payment for guarding while Mr. Jougasaki was out continued. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Mr. Jougasaki came back, I would be quickly thrown out of the room. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those days... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you lately? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you've been moving up in the world. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you mean. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Kaori-san's bodyguard, isn't that right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do you know that? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not underestimate my information-gathering network. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki-san may act that way, but he's really pure-hearted. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a very refined kind of love. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a far cry from some "dutch wife." 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very high-quality product called a "love doll." 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:09:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that it's designed to be loved and held dear by its owner. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boor like you who thinks of it as nothing more 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than a tool to satisfy one's sexual desire wouldn't understand. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, right now! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then stay silent for eternity! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll have to decline. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't chat, I'll be so lonely I'll die! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good to me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, I won't die as long as I'm making some idle chatter. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no empathy for a soulless being like you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be a bit more honest with yourself, will you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jougasaki seemed to be busy at the moment shooting a film. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a modern remake of Alexander the Great 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which was supposed to be the culmination of his work or something. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within his circle he was very popular and charismatic, 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but his favorite was, of course, Kaori-san. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm counting on you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around this time Mr. Jougasaki would be out of his room continuously, 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and feeling sorry for the girl, I took tender care of her... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, of course, she was just a doll. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am exchanging letters with a real flesh and blood woman.  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She always answers me back.  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how beautiful Kaori-san looks to the eye, she will never respond.  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Hey...  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exquisite workmanship,  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the delicate and lovely world Jougasaki had set up,  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,made me think of her as a real person occasionally.  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ news is going great, don't you think?  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you, Hanuki-san.  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanuki-san is a dental hygienist and an older member of the English Conversation circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It became a habit of ours to go to a café after each session.  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seemed like she only drank alcohol with people she knew well,  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I had not yet been asked out for drinks.  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was wavering between the perverted dentist, Kubouzuka,  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who continuously asked her out, and a boyfriend that neglected her.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally received a letter from my pen-pal Keiko-san saying she wanted to meet.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that's proof that my literary skills  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at lighting a maiden's heart on fire were nothing to scoff at.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I was not able to meet her.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because the me within the letters was ever so slightly embellished from the me in reality.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that's what I envision my ideal self to be,  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it will take a bit of time for the current me to catch up.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency!  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, your place stinks!  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my place isn't safe.  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on to Kaori here for a while, will you?  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori, I'm sorry. I know this is a filthy place, but please endure it for a little while.  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you the same hourly rate as before, at 24 hours a day. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I don't have the cash on hand, so please allow me to do a direct bank deposit.  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was how Kaori-san and I began living together.  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, wasn't Mr. Jougasaki thinking a bit too little of me?  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be that as it may, I never even dreamed that  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,such a sweet campus life would be visited upon me.  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In these two past years I'd spent living uneventfully,  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had never experienced such a brilliant event.  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This and that... And two of each, please.  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I returned from class, Kaori-san was waiting for me in my room.  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That alone made the days enjoyable.  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was as if an intellectual, raven-haired maiden  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whose dreams were filled with novels had borrowed a corner of my room.  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of these days she will no longer be here, will she?  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say love comes on all forms,  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it is dangerous to become lost in the maze of such an insular love.  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I became fearful that I could no longer find the exit, I pressed deeper along the path.  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am pleased to eat ramen for the first time.  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wished to eat it once.  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure whether it's to your taste, however...  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's quite beautiful, yes?  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, she's Jougasaki's girlfriend, so please keep it a secret that we came here to eat.  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, eat up.  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you ate ramen! I can smell it on you!  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat in your room! Eat outside!  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But well, I'm not getting any younger.  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just been doing what I felt like up till now,  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I finish this movie I'm filming, I'm thinking of settling down.  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll graduate, get a job, and then live once again with Kaori.  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been a great help.  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come to pick up Kaori soon.  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally I received an ultimatum from Keiko-san.  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't meet with her this time, all communication will likely cease.  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was still not the man able to see Keiko-san.  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wanna go for some drinks?  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a report I need to write today...  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:15:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Good luck on your report!  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally I was asked out for drinks by Hanuki-san as proof that we were close,  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet I ended up going home.  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because tonight was the night Jougasaki was coming to pick up Kaori-san.  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I aim to become come Renaissance man of the sexual arts,  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must narrow it down to one of them.  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-san, please wait a little while!  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a matter of life and death!  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow Hanuki-san to be ruined by some perverted dentist's intentions!  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, at the hotel's lounge I was met with an expected turn of events.  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For there in front of me was Mr. Jougasaki.  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disgusted that he would try and place his hands on Hanuki-san while he was still with Kaori-san,  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I had no choice but to win this drinking battle!  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I was victorious!  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I was met with yet another unexpected turn of events.  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think you're doing?  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to do this!  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our once in a lifetime chance!  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.43,0:16:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it... Kaori's the only one for me....  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori!  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori!  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body shakes thinking this might be the last time I hear your voice.  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I am loved once more by Jougasaki, a different me will surely sprout.  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The me who is here now only exists in front of you.  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori...  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me with you and escape.  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, please!  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:17:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We're eloping. Thank you for everything. - Kaori," eh?  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Jougasaki-san?  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-san is getting wet!  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kaori-san...  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm glad. I've never gotten wet from the rain before.  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-san...  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, student...  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old woman!  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Student, what might you wish to ask?  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't asked you anything!  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You are dissatisfied, yes?  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I had no idea what you're talking about!  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, opportunity is always dangling in front of you.  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.63,0:18:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please grab on to it.  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 7,000 yen.  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the rain lets up, 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll head to Kyoto station and buy train tickets to as far away as we can.  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll head to a country at the end of the earth,  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and live in a small town in a small house...  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working in a strange land will surely be tough,  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but seeing your smile when I come home will give me cheer.  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before long, we'll have a child,  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your parents who were against this will surely come to accept me.  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The days and months pass by and at length we have grandchildren.  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I realize I have lived only for that day, tears fall from my eyes.  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the happiest days of my life.  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But suddenly you fall ill, and I grasp your hand, nursing you.  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiling, you say "I'm so glad I met you."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no, that's what I should be saying!  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we promise that I'd be the first to go?  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just so glad we were able to be together!  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this isn't an opportunity, then what is?  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, this here's a 100% full-blow opportunity!  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at her face, she's waiting for you!  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-san isn't like that!  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how high-class her face looks,  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,inside her heart is the same burning passion that's inside yours!  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie!  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no it isn't!  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think she came with you?  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always with you!  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? She's been looking at you the whole time...  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we part, I want to share your warmth...  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you let me feel like I am loved?  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-san, but...  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that to you this isn't passionate, burning love.  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now the warmth of your hand  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the one thing that can make me feel like I'm alive.  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't? Is it because I'm not a real person?  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a doll without a heart?  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kaori-san! That's not it!  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also...  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too beautiful!  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away, you coward!  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to spend the rest of your life a pitiful late-bloomer?  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with being called a "safe bet"?  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about her shame!  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she wants you to thrust your burning passion upon her! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been waiting this whole time! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I'm sorry.  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am, after all, a doll. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then make her a woman!  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't do it!  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you come and do it!  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it... I'll do it for him...  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me!  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! What are you doing?  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-san! Johnny, stop it!  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori!  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:20:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori, Kaori!  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sick bastard!  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it should be.  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had almost lost my pure heart.  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would never have been able to love Kaori-san in a pure manner.  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a path unable to be tread by we normal people.  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki and Kaori-san, keep going down that path together!  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Keiko-san waited for me at the place she said?  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps she was the preferable choice?  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to return to that scene once again!  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retake!  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}I want to meet Keiko-san!  
